    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You cause the target to relive bad memories from all those it has killed. If the target has never killed anyone, it is therefore immune to this technique. The subject must save each round to avoid suffering a cumulative -1 morale penalty to attack rolls, skill checks and saves, and a cumulative +1 rage bonus to weapon damage rolls against you.<br><br>The morale penalties persist for 1 minute after the technique ends, though the rage bonus ends when the technique does.</p>\n\n\n\n",
